OL,6,FA shoplifter who drove his car into a
OL,7,Ffarm shop worker as he tried to block
OL,8,Fhis escape has been jailed.
OL,10,FDramatic CCTV footage captured Alan
OL,11,FLewis, 58, driving directly into the
OL,12,Fman after stealing nearly #900 worth
OL,13,Fof stock from Mainsgill Farmshop in
OL,14,FRichmond, North Yorkshire, on
OL,15,FSaturday, 23 November 2024.
OL,17,FIt shows the employee being carried
OL,18,Faway on the bonnet of the Vauxhall
OL,19,FCorsa.
