OL,6,FThe footage has been viewed millions
OL,7,Fof times online.
OL,9,FLewis, 58, from Goole, pleaded guilty
OL,10,Fto shoplifting, dangerous driving and
OL,11,Fdriving while disqualified and without
OL,12,Finsurance.
OL,14,FOn Friday at York Crown Court, his
OL,15,Factions were described by a judge as
OL,16,F"utterly despicable".
OL,18,FThe court heard he had 33 previous
OL,19,Fconvictions, many for driving offences.
